OL,3,CTeenage boy denies murdering Aria
OL,4,CThorpe, 9, in Weston-super-Mare
OL,6,FA teenage boy has pleaded not guilty
OL,7,Fto murdering a nine-year-old girl in
OL,8,FWeston-super-Mare in December 2025.
OL,10,FThe 16-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,11,Fbecause of his young age, is charged
OL,12,Fwith killing Aria Thorpe.
OL,14,FAria was pronounced dead after police
OL,15,Fwere called to the Mead Vale area of
OL,16,Fthe North Somerset town at 6.09pm on
OL,17,F15 December.
OL,19,FAvon Coroner's Court previously heard
OL,20,FAria died from a single stab wound to
OL,21,Fher chest at her home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
