OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774627872
OL,3,CTeenage boy denies murdering Aria
OL,4,CThorpe, 9, in Weston-super-Mare
OL,6,FOn Friday, 27 March, the boy appeared
OL,7,Fbefore Bristol Crown Court and replied
OL,8,F"not guilty" after the single charge
OL,9,Fagainst him was read out.
OL,11,FProsecuting, Ray Tully KC told the
OL,12,Fcourt: "The matter is set for trial on
OL,13,F15 June, with a time estimate of two
OL,14,Fweeks."
OL,16,FAndrew Langdon KC appeared for the
OL,17,Fdefence during the hearing, which
OL,18,Flasted 20 minutes.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]tD@HOUvD@GO]
