PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774627872
OL,3,CTeenage boy denies murdering Aria
OL,4,CThorpe, 9, in Weston-super-Mare
OL,6,FJudge Martin Picton said reporting
OL,7,Frestrictions preventing the identity
OL,8,Fof the defendant from being published
OL,9,Fwould continue, due to his age.
OL,11,FIn tributes issued after her death,
OL,12,FAria's father Tom Thorpe described her
OL,13,Fas a "brave, kind-hearted and a
OL,14,Fbeautiful innocent soul".
OL,16,FAria's family on her mother's side
OL,17,Fsaid she was "the most beautiful
OL,18,Flittle soul ` happy-go-lucky, full of
OL,19,Flight, and joy".
OL,26,@uD@FOUvD@XO]yD@NOU{D@OO]
