OL,3,CTeenage boy denies murdering Aria
OL,4,CThorpe, 9, in Weston-super-Mare
OL,6,FThe boy, who was remanded into
OL,7,Fcustody, will stand trial at Bristol
OL,8,FCrown Court on 15 June, 2026.
